    "description": "<!-- MOBILE DESCRIPTION -->\n<div style=\"display:none\">\n<div vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n<span property=\"description\">The ASR Outdoor pocket aluminum mini sluice box is ideal for fine gold recovery, This is the perfect companion for you to use while processing your gold concentrate. Ideal for fine sand processing after classifying raw sediment and gold paydirt through a 1/20\" material classifier sifting screen, the V-shape grooved rubber sluice matting is sure to pick up all of your fine gold pickers and small gold flake. Just spoon feed your sifted material through the channel and provide a small amount of water flow and watch the gold flakes appear on the ribbed rubber matting.<br><br>This mini pocket sluice box is small; at only 12\" in length with a 3.5\" wide channel it is one of the smallest prospecting tools that is easy to carry; incredibly lightweight, easy to assemble, with no tools required to assemble</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- MAIN DESCRIPTION -->\n\n\n\t<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n\t<style type=\"text/css\">\n\t\t/* FONTS AND COLORS */\n\t\tbody {\n\t\t\tfont-family: Arial,sans-serif;\n\t\t\tfont-size: 14px;\n\t\t\tline-height: 1.428571429;\n\t\t\tcolor: #333;\n\t\t\tbackground-color: white;\n\t\t}\n\t\th1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {\n\t\t\tcolor: black;\n\t\t}\n\t\tp {\n\t\t\twhite-space: pre-line;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.navbar a, .navbar a:active, .navbar a:hover, .navbar a:visited {\n\t\t\tcolor: #333;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t.product-specs {\n\t\t\tbackground-color: #f1f1f1;\n\t\t\tpadding: 1em;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.product-specs td {\n\t\t\tfont-size:12px;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.attr-left {\n\t\t\tmin-width:6em;\n\t\t\tfont-weight:bold;\n\t\t\tvertical-align:top;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.attr-right {\n\t\t\tvertical-align:top;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\tdiv.footer {\n\t\t\tborder-top: 1px solid #f1f1f1;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t.navbar-default {\n\t\t\tbackground-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(top, #ffffff 0%, #f2f2f2 100%);\n\t