td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">855569003937</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">Features:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">NO ASSEMBLY REQUIRED: Ready to use out of the box; Uses wing nut closures for easy set up; No tools required; Run gold paydirt and processed concentrate to maximize your gold recovery efforts</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">COMPACT AND PORTABLE: At only 12” length by 3.5” wide with 1.5\" high channel walls, this aluminum pocket mini sluice box is easy to pack up in your hiking backpack for your next gold prospecting adventure</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">RUBBER SLUICE BOX MATTING: Includes V-Shape ribbed rubber sluice box matting. Optional woven vinyl miners moss carpet can be installed under the rustproof angled mesh channel inserts if desired (not included)</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">WEATHERPROOF: Constructed from rust resistant aluminum this mini pocket sluice box is durable and built to last; ideal for fine gold recovery</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">BEGINNER PROSPECTING: Makes a great camping or outdoor activity for adults or kids; portable gold prospecting that wont break the bank and catches fine gold flakes</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1>ASR Outdoor Gold Panning Aluminum Mini Sluice Box with Rubber Matting, 12 Inch</h1>\n\t\t\t<h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">31.99</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<p>The ASR Outdoor pocket aluminum mini sluice box is ideal for fine gold recovery, This is the perfect companion for you to use while processing your gold concentrate. Ideal for fine sand processing after classifying raw sediment and gold paydirt through a 1/20\" material classifier sifting screen, the V-shape grooved rubber sluice matting is sure to pick up all of your fine gold pickers and small gold flake. Just spoon feed your sifted material through the channel and provide a small amount of water flow and watch the gold flakes appear on the ribbed rubber matting.\n\nThis mini pocket sluice box is small; at only 12\" in length with a 3.5\" wide channel it is one of the smallest prospecting tools that is easy to carry; incredibly lightweight, easy to assemble, with no tools required to assemble. It comes out of the box, ready to use. It is equipped complete with angled mesh and high quality V-Shape ribbed rubber mat. Woven vinyl miners moss can also be used in this mini sluice box and can be switched out simply by removing the wingnut and washer that holds everything in place. Use small glass collection vials for your recovered fine gold found through your gold panning efforts.\n\nSure this ASR Outdoor mini sluice box could be used in the field while you survey new gold prospecting claims before packing in your large equipment. But it is much more practical for use at home or in the foreman trailer to evaluate your concentrate. Likewise, this is a fun unit for beginners and classrooms to jump start their luck and understanding of gold prospecting with mail order pay dirt, without breaking the bank first. It is made from rust resistant aluminum and will last for many years to come as this is a high-quality gold prospecting and mining equipment tool.\n\nHave a complete compact gold prospecting sluice box anywhere you are with this rugged piece of gold prospecting equipment by ASR Outdoor.</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-100\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&amp;sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t<p>© 2026</p></div></div>",
